'''統計師'''是指从事[[統計|統計]]理论或统计应用工作的人。統計師通常将统计知识与其他学科的專業知识相结合。[[私营部门|私营部门]]和[[公共部门|公共部门]]會聘請一名統計師為正式僱員，統計師也可以前往[[私营部门|私营部门]]和[[公共部门|公共部门]]兼職，充當一名统计顾问<ref name="ONET">{{Cite web|title=O*NET OnLine: 15-2041.00 - Statisticians|url=https://www.onetonline.org/link/summary/15-2041.00|accessdate=29 January 2017|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404005730/https://www.onetonline.org/link/summary/15-2041.00|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Royal Statistical Society StatsLife Types of Job|url=https://www.statslife.org.uk/careers/types-of-job|accessdate=29 January 2017|archive-date=2018-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030014222/https://www.statslife.org.uk/careers/types-of-job|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在美国，統計師一般擁有统计专业或相关领域的[[硕士|硕士学位]]或[[哲學博士|博士学位]]。<ref name="ONET"/>

